    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在安排右边俄罗斯方块的同时，需要兼顾左边的三消。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两种颜色的叠加变成新的颜色，横竖三个或以上相同颜色完成三消，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291240/extras/1e93936146046032d2da5d89474b9695.webp?t=1741258027\" width=64 height=42 /></span>示意图表示红色钻石叠加红色方块会变成白色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果一定步数内没有及时完成三消会收到惩罚的噢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291240/extras/27df86ddecb421df249167bc8852966e.webp?t=1741258027\" width=36 height=35 /></span>红心表示还有多少次会积累到大的惩罚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惩罚是会递增的，而且会大到你无法承受！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291240/extras/9bc0ff486fe0267d5273cdff4fa89a3c.webp?t=1741258027\" width=36 height=35 /></span>表示红心全部耗尽后，会有在右边底部增加一行的惩罚，然后红心全部恢复，但下次惩罚会加重。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果这只是个开始，那就用你非凡的大脑挑战更高的难度吧：取消合成的提示；右边方块不再静止不动；遮住一些下面的方块。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消除不定期闪烁的钻石，你可以获得一些有用的道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291240/extras/e169ab361cca12c90f3b999a8ef6df1a.webp?t=1741258027\" width=27 height=36 /></span>炸弹可以帮助消除右边最上面一行或几行的方块。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ASDW控制方向，QE旋转，空格键落定方块。本游戏支持手柄操作，但需要设置。</p>",
